          "text": "Best-effort delivery"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "Minimal overhead"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "Reliable delivery",
      "explanation": "UDP is an unreliable protocol. It does not provide acknowledgment, retransmission, or sequencing of packets.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
